<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sports - Integration Fest</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; overflow-x: hidden; background: #000; color: #fff; }
        
        .navbar { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 1000; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2); padding: 20px 0; }
        .nav-container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 0 20px; }
        .nav-logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #f093fb 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; text-decoration: none; }
        .nav-menu { display: flex; list-style: none; gap: 30px; align-items: center; }
        .nav-item { position: relative; }
        .nav-link { color: rgba(184, 197, 255, 0.9); text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; transition: color 0.3s ease; padding: 10px 15px; display: block; }
        .nav-link:hover { color: #667eea; }
        .dropdown { position: relative; }
        .dropdown-menu { position: absolute; top: 100%; left: 0; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3); border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 0; min-width: 200px; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transform: translateY(-10px); transition: all 0.3s ease; margin-top: 10px; }
        .dropdown:hover .dropdown-menu { opacity: 1; visibility: visible; transform: translateY(0); }
        .dropdown-item { padding: 12px 20px; color: rgba(184, 197, 255, 0.9); text-decoration: none; display: block; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .dropdown-item:hover { background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1); color: #667eea; }
        .mobile-menu-toggle { display: none; background: none; border: none; color: #667eea; font-size: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; }
        
        .page-header { padding: 120px 20px 60px; text-align: center; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 1) 70%); }
        .page-title { font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 900; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 50%, #f093fb 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .page-subtitle { font-size: 1.3rem; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-style: italic; color: rgba(136, 146, 176, 0.8); }
        
        .sports-section { padding: 80px 20px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .sports-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; margin-bottom: 60px; }
        .sport-card { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02); border-radius: 8px; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.15); transition: all 0.3s ease; cursor: pointer; }
        .sport-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04); border-color: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3); box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2); }
        .sport-icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px; display: block; }
        .sport-name { font-size: 1.8rem; color: #b8c5ff; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .sport-description { color: #8892b0; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .sport-details { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #667eea; }
        .sport-details span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .mobile-menu-toggle { display: block; }
            .nav-menu { position: fixed; top: 70px; left: -100%; flex-direction: column; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.98); width: 100%; height: calc(100vh - 70px); padding: 30px 0; gap: 0; transition: left 0.3s ease; align-items: flex-start; }
            .nav-menu.active { left: 0; }
            .nav-item { width: 100%; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1); }
            .nav-link { padding: 20px 30px; }
            .dropdown-menu { position: static; opacity: 1; visibility: visible; transform: none; border: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1); border-radius: 0; margin-top: 0; max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.3s ease; }
            .dropdown.active .dropdown-menu { max-height: 300px; }
            .dropdown > .nav-link::after { content: ' ▼'; font-size: 0.8rem; }
            .dropdown.active > .nav-link::after { content: ' ▲'; }
            .page-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .page-subtitle { font-size: 1rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="index.html" class="nav-logo">∫ Integration Fest</a>
            <button class="mobile-menu-toggle" id="mobileMenuToggle">☰</button>
            <ul class="nav-menu" id="navMenu">
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="index.html" class="nav-link">Home</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item dropdown" id="techDropdown">
                    <a href="#" class="nav-link">Tech</a>
                    <div class="dropdown-menu">
                        <a href="#" class="dropdown-item">SPARQ</a>
                        <a href="#" class="dropdown-item">MTRP</a>
                        <a href="#" class="dropdown-item">Integration Bee</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="cultural.html" class="nav-link">Cultural</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="sports.html" class="nav-link">Sports</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="gallery.html" class="nav-link">Gallery</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="page-header">
        <h1 class="page-title">Sports Events</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">∫ (Athletic Excellence) → Championship Glory</p>
    </div>

    <section class="sports-section">
        <div class="sports-grid">
            <div class="sport-card">
                <span class="sport-icon">🏏</span>
                <h3 class="sport-name">Cricket</h3>
                <p class="sport-description">Experience the thrill of competitive cricket with teams from across institutions battling for supremacy.</p>
                <div class="sport-details">
                    <span>⏰ Date: March 15-17, 2025</span>
                    <span>📍 Venue: Main Sports Ground</span>
                    <span>👥 Team Size: 11 players</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sport-card">
                <span class="sport-icon">⚽</span>
                <h3 class="sport-name">Football</h3>
                <p class="sport-description">Join the beautiful game! Showcase your skills and teamwork in our prestigious football tournament.</p>
                <div class="sport-details">
                    <span>⏰ Date: March 18-20, 2025</span>
                    <span>📍 Venue: Football Field</span>
                    <span>👥 Team Size: 11 players</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sport-card">
                <span class="sport-icon">♟️</span>
                <h3 class="sport-name">Chess</h3>
                <p class="sport-description">Test your strategic thinking in intense chess battles. From beginners to grandmasters, all are welcome.</p>
                <div class="sport-details">
                    <span>⏰ Date: March 16-18, 2025</span>
                    <span>📍 Venue: Indoor Hall A</span>
                    <span>👥 Individual Event</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sport-card">
                <span class="sport-icon">🏓</span>
                <h3 class="sport-name">Table Tennis</h3>
                <p class="sport-description">Fast-paced action awaits! Compete in singles and doubles matches in our table tennis championship.</p>
                <div class="sport-details">
                    <span>⏰ Date: March 19-20, 2025</span>
                    <span>📍 Venue: Indoor Sports Complex</span>
                    <span>👥 Singles & Doubles</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sport-card">
                <span class="sport-icon">🃏</span>
                <h3 class="sport-name">Bridge</h3>
                <p class="sport-description">Master the art of partnership and strategy in this classic card game tournament.</p>
                <div class="sport-details">
                    <span>⏰ Date: March 17-19, 2025</span>
                    <span>📍 Venue: Indoor Hall B</span>
                    <span>👥 Pairs Event</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sport-card">
                <span class="sport-icon">🏃</span>
                <h3 class="sport-name">Athletics</h3>
                <p class="sport-description">Sprint, jump, and throw your way to glory in our comprehensive athletics championship.</p>
                <div class="sport-details">
                    <span>⏰ Date: March 21-22, 2025</span>
                    <span>📍 Venue: Athletics Track</span>
                    <span>👥 Individual & Team Events</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('mobileMenuToggle').onclick = () => document.getElementById('navMenu').classList.toggle('active');
        document.getElementById('techDropdown').onclick = (e) => {
            if (window.innerWidth <= 768 && e.target.classList.contains('nav-link')) {
                e.preventDefault();
                document.getElementById('techDropdown').classList.toggle('active');
            }
        };
        document.onclick = (e) => { if (!e.target.closest('.navbar')) document.getElementById('navMenu').classList.remove('active'); };
    </script>
</body>
</html>
